AirportFaster — UX Architecture & Product Flows

Version: 1.1 · Last updated: 2026-05-14 · See "Document Review & Corrections" at end.

Document Purpose

This document translates the AirportFaster business requirements into practical UX architecture, user journeys, page structure, product flows, and operational flows.

It acts as the bridge between the BRD and the next phases:

* UI/UX wireframes
* System architecture
* Database architecture
* API architecture
* Development planning

