8. Booking Status Lifecycle

Main Booking Statuses

Draft

Booking started but not completed.

Pending Payment

Customer reached checkout but payment not completed.

Paid

Payment completed.

Pending Supplier Assignment

Booking paid but supplier not yet assigned.

Supplier Assigned

Supplier selected internally.

Pending Supplier Confirmation

Supplier has been contacted but not confirmed.

Confirmed

Supplier confirmed service.

In Progress

Service is currently being delivered.

Completed

Service completed successfully.

Cancelled

Booking cancelled.

Refunded

Refund processed.

Failed / Incident

Operational issue occurred.

