29. Final UX Principle

Every page and flow must support one of three goals:

1. Help the customer book quickly and confidently.
2. Help the operations team control every booking and supplier action.
3. Help AirportFaster grow through SEO, AEO, and AI discoverability.

If a feature does not support one of these goals, it should not be included in the MVP.

